This is a Next.js 14 app router project using TypeScript.
Database: Supabase (Postgres). Always use the Supabase JS client from @/lib/supabase.ts. Never use an ORM.
Payments: Stripe. Always validate webhook signatures. Use test mode keys during development.
Email: Resend.
All environment variables come from process.env — never hardcode secrets.
API routes live in /app/api/ as route.ts files using Next.js route handlers.
Always return typed JSON responses from API routes.
Validate all incoming request bodies using Zod before processing.
Database types come from @/types/database.ts.
Never generate UI components or pages unless explicitly asked.
Keep all business logic in /lib/ files, not inside route handlers.tu